snippet.title: Birth - Official Xbox Release Date Trailer | ID@Xbox Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Birth will be available on Xbox on July 28, 2023. Watch the latest trailer for Birth to see gameplay, puzzles, and the mysterious world filled with skeletal residents of this adventure puzzle game. In Birth, you will construct a creature from spare bones and organs found around the city in order to quell your loneliness.
